('S21-E2', 21, 2, 443, 'Bart Gets a ''Z''', 'When Bart''s prank gets Ms. Krabappel fired from Springfield Elementary School, he tries to make it up to her without letting her know that he was responsible.', '2009-10-04', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjM3MDI4NDI1NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjIwODQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.7, 952),
('S21-E3', 21, 3, 444, 'The Great Wife Hope', 'Marge takes on the owner of an ultimate fighting league in the ring in order to get the sport banned in Springfield.', '2009-10-11', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzE5NjUzMjY3MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODEwODQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.3, 871),
('S21-E4', 21, 4, 445, 'Treehouse of Horror XX', 'Lisa becomes livid with Miss Hoover, and in a series of homages to classic Hitchcock sets out for deadly revenge. Next, Krusty''s latest fast-food sandwich transforms news anchor Kent Brockman into an enraged zombie and twenty-eight days later, cannibal zombies have overrun Springfield. In the final frightening fable, Homer accidentally falls through a trapdoor in Moe''s tavern and impales himself on the pipes of Moe''s microbrewery. Moe serves the barflies a glass of delicious beer flavored with Homer''s blood and Homer, now half-man, half-brewing apparatus, returns for ...', '2009-10-18', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2VkYWQzN2UtYmM4Ny00YzU3LThiNjMtZTM1NDQwMGY1N2YyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjAwODA4Mw@@._V1_UY126_CR15,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 7.2, 1079),
('S21-E5', 21, 5, 446, 'The Devil Wears Nada', 'Marge rediscovers her sexuality after appearing in a racy calendar, but Homer is too tired to respond to her advances because he is being worked to death by his new boss, Carl.', '2009-11-15', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTgwMjgwMzI3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ5MTQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.6, 852),
('S21-E6', 21, 6, 447, 'Pranks and Greens', 'Bart meets the boy responsible for the greatest prank in Springfield Elementary School history, and discovers that he''s now a 19-year-old loser. Meanwhile, Marge is scolded for providing unhealthy snacks for Maggie''s play group.', '2009-11-22', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTU5NjcyOTIwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTk5MTQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.6, 836),
('S21-E7', 21, 7, 448, 'Rednecks and Broomsticks', 'Homer becomes an expert on moonshine when he starts hanging out with Cletus after he saves the Simpsons'' lives, while Lisa becomes friends with three teenage Wiccans.', '2009-11-29', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTUxOTEzNDY5OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTE3MzQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.9, 846),
('S21-E8', 21, 8, 449, 'Oh Brother, Where Bart Thou?', 'Bart becomes jealous of Maggie and Lisa''s special bond as sisters, so he goes to an orphanage and "adopts" a little brother.', '2009-12-13', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjE2ODEwOTAwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjczNzQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 7.2, 892),
('S21-E9', 21, 9, 450, 'Thursdays with Abie', 'Homer becomes jealous when a syndicated newspaper columnist begins publishing Grandpa''s stories, while Bart is assigned to take care of the class''s stuffed sheep for the weekend.', '2010-01-03', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzY2Mjk4Nzg4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzkzMzQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.6, 784),
('S21-E10', 21, 10, 451, 'Once Upon a Time in Springfield', 'The antagonism between Krusty and the new female co-star forced upon him soon turns to romance, while a headhunter encourages Homer, Lenny and Carl to take a job at another nuclear power plant.', '2010-01-10', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjgxMjkzNjM1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTY1MzQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.6, 843),
('S21-E11', 21, 11, 452, 'Million Dollar Maybe', 'Homer can''t tell Marge he won the lottery because he was supposed to be giving a wedding toast when he bought the ticket. But Bart soon finds out where he''s hiding the money and begins to blackmail him.', '2010-01-31', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODEzNjI4Mjg2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTUxNTM2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 7.0, 838),
('S21-E12', 21, 12, 453, 'Boy Meets Curl', 'Homer and Marge become members of the U.S. Olympic curling team. At the games, Lisa becomes addicted to collecting pins, and Bart tries to save her.', '2010-02-14', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTAyMjY1NzI2OTVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDA2MTUzNjIx._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.9, 864),
