('S21-E15', 21, 15, 456, 'Stealing First Base', 'Bart gets Springfield Elementary School in legal trouble when he kisses the enigmatic daughter of two lawyers, while Lisa is depressed about being ostracized because she is smart.', '2010-03-21', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjE2NTk5ODcyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTM1MzQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.9, 876),
