('S21-E17', 21, 17, 458, 'American History X-cellent', 'Mr Burns is sent to prison for art theft, where a scary inmate introduces him to religion. Meanwhile Smithers becomes the boss at the plant, and Bart and Lisa try to share an ant farm.', '2010-04-11', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjMzMTg3MzIxOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODkzODM2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.7, 783),
