('S22-E4', 22, 4, 468, 'Treehouse of Horror XXI', 'A Satanic board game causes other popular board games to come to life, Homer and Marge rescue a possible killer and let him on their boat, and a parody of "Twilight" where Lisa falls for a young vampire.', '2010-11-07', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc1MTI3MDAzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTYyOTQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 7.0, 1048),
('S22-E5', 22, 5, 469, 'Lisa Simpson, This Isn''t Your Life', 'When Lisa discovers that Marge was also a model student, she tries to find out where everything changed so that she doesn''t repeat her mistakes. Meanwhile, a series of chance accidents cause Bart to replace Nelson as school bully.', '2010-11-14', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQ5NjUwMjU1N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTM1OTkwNA@@._V1_UY126_CR2,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 7.1, 819),
