('S22-E10', 22, 10, 474, 'Moms I''d Like to Forget', 'Bart sets out to uncover the origins of a sword-shaped scar on his hand; Marge reconnects with three friends she fell out with years ago.', '2011-01-09', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTkxMTk1NDU1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDcyOTQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.2, 749),
