('S22-E16', 22, 16, 480, 'A Midsummer''s Nice Dreams', 'After Tommy Chong walks away from the Cheech & Chong reunion tour, Homer goes on the road as his replacement. Meanwhile, Marge tries to help the cat lady with her hoarding problem.', '2011-03-13', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQxNTE2Nzc4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjgyOTQ2MjE@._V1_UX224_CR0,0,224,126_AL_.jpg', 6.0, 775),
